•
FR-A6: Admin dashboard with KPIs and filters: orders, invoices, revenues, payouts, vendors, app downloads, inventory levels, user activity, returns/refunds, sales by category/brand/time period.
•
FR-A7: Admin can manage payment gateway account(s) and bank account settings for receiving funds (store merchant/account details).
•
FR-A8: Admin can block/unblock any customer or vendor account (immediate effect).
•
FR-A9: Admin can create and manage categories/sub-categories and units (pcs, box, carton).
•
FR-A10: Admin can view logs / activities and export reports (PDF) — orders, payouts, inventory, vendor.
•
FR-A11: Admin can configure system parameters: order timeout for vendor acceptance, proximity radius, automatic reassign rules, tax rates, shipping charges, coupon codes.
2.2 Customer (Mobile App)
•
FR-C1: Customer installs app and registers with mobile number + OTP verification (SMS OTP). Optional: email.
•
FR-C2: Customer can search/browse categories, filter by brand, price, compatibility, delivery time.
•
FR-C3: Product detail page: images, price, unit, stock status, service time.
•
FR-C4: Add items to a shopping cart; adjust quantity and unit.
•
FR-C5: Customers can store multiple shipping addresses in address book (labelled home, work, garage, etc).
•
FR-C6: Checkout flow with selection of shipping address, payment option, order review, apply coupon code.
•
FR-C7: Payment via integrated payment gateway (cards, UPI, wallets, netbanking). Payments go to admin’s merchant account; system records transaction/invoice.
•
FR-C8: Order confirmation, order tracking (status updates), order history & invoices. Cancel / return request flow (policy governed).
•
FR-C9: Raise support issues for an order (text + attach photo). View status of issues.
•
FR-C10: Chat with assigned vendor (in-app chat) for order support. Chat is one-to-one between customer and assigned vendor only for that order.
•
FR-C11: Push notifications for OTP, order status updates, vendor messages, delivery ETA, invoice.
